WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.315
As soon as you open IEFP CRM, the Dashboard gives you the state of the business at a glance:

00:00:06.315 --> 00:00:10.159
won revenue, average deal, pipeline and conversion rate.

00:00:10.159 --> 00:00:12.493
With one click you pick the period

00:00:12.493 --> 00:00:14.003
quarter, month or year

00:00:14.003 --> 00:00:19.220
and every metric, chart and the calendar adjust to what you want to analyse.
